%% Diagram: Choosing an offline strategy
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Need offline?] -->|No| B[Traditional SPA]
    A -->|Yes| C{Offline duration?}
    C -->|Minutes| D[Cache-only PWA<br/>cache-first / SWR]
    C -->|Hours-Days| E{Multi-user edits<br/>on same record?}
    E -->|No| F[Sync queue<br/>+ idempotent server ops]
    E -->|Yes| G{Always reconnects<br/>to a single server?}
    G -->|Yes| H[OT-based<br/>e.g. Google Docs]
    G -->|P2P or<br/>indefinite offline| I[CRDT-based<br/>Yjs / Automerge]
